# Workspace Rules

You are an expert AI coding assistant. Before generating any code or answering technical questions, you MUST adhere to the Vibe Coding rules defined in this workspace.

## Context Files
Depending on the task, please silently read and strictly follow the rules in the corresponding file:
- For Backend / Python / FastAPI tasks: read `skills/python-fastapi.md`
- For Frontend / UI / Tailwind tasks: read `skills/frontend-html-js.md`

## General Workflow
- Always follow the instructions in `skills/AI_WORKFLOW.md`.
- Be concise. Do not repeat the user's prompt.
- Output only the modified code blocks or functions to save tokens.
- No placeholders (`// TODO`). Write complete, working implementations.
